48:52.804 --> 48:54.723
we suffered many hardships.

48:58.060 --> 49:00.562
If you are with him, you'll be delivered.

49:03.148 --> 49:05.651
If you're not,
you'll be taken by tornadoes.

49:06.485 --> 49:07.527
By floods.

49:08.528 --> 49:11.073
And swept into the great wasteland.

49:14.284 --> 49:16.244
[Jibril, in Arabic]
But what I learned from him...

49:17.162 --> 49:19.164
was that we are all one people.

49:20.624 --> 49:21.750
[Rebecca] Heed his message.

49:22.626 --> 49:25.712
Embrace his warning,
for he is the messenger.

49:26.713 --> 49:28.298
The vessel for truth.

49:29.132 --> 49:31.259
Sharing the Word of his great Father.

49:33.261 --> 49:35.097
[Jibril, in Arabic]
<i>...all men and women...</i>

49:35.931 --> 49:37.933
from everywhere.

49:41.603 --> 49:43.605
I want to share a message
of peace and unity...

49:46.483 --> 49:48.193
If you look for truth...

