If you look for comfort...

50:29.067 --> 50:31.153
[crowd yelling]

50:35.240 --> 50:36.074
[Rebecca] <i>al-Masih...</i>

50:44.166 --> 50:45.751
The eye of...

50:49.129 --> 50:50.297
Jibril...

50:54.634 --> 50:55.594
Samer...

51:03.560 --> 51:05.187
The eye of the storm.

